snippet.title: Dr. Robotnik's Creature Capture: A Spin-off Sonic Hack
snippet.description:
This video showcases Dr. Robotnik's Creature Capture, a spin-off type Sonic the Hedgehog 1 rom hack where you take control of Dr. Robotnik (Eggman) and capture all the animals in the stages before the time runs out. Made by MarkeyJester & Many others.MarkeyJester + Many others
#SonicHacks #SonicSpinOff #SonicTheHedgehog
